This device is new and comes with Samsung charger and wired earbuds and all info and directions etc. This should be listed as "NEW", however the  requirements define new as factory sealed and despite how carefully I pealed back the seals to look at the device, so it's no longer "factory sealed"; and as such I had to listed it as "Mint" but it is clearly NEW. I had the device unlocked by T-Mobile, so you should be able to use it on any network you choose but before you buy, check the IMEI  number on the network you plan on using it on because I'm new to this technology. The screen protector that is currently on it was installed just a couple of weeks ago so it's in great shape too. Physically, the device is a total stunner!
The internals are in great shape as well. I barely used the selfie cam, so that mechanism is like new. I rarely ever charged the battery over 85%, so it's also in great shape (see attached screenshot). Also, I kept the screen brightness low or on auto, so there's no burn-in. It is running the latest Beta 18 software, so you will have the latest software features before they make their way to the official builds.
A OnePlus Nylon Bumper case, the original Warp charger, and a Dash charger with cable for your car is included. Also, the phone and all accessories have been cleaned and disinfected for your peace of mind.
Thank you!
Damage: Only slight hazing around bezels from plugging-in charging cable and occasionally removing case to clean device. You honestly have to look really hard to even see it at all but would rate that area like a 9/10. As for the screen and glass back, there are zero imperfections, 10/10.
